channel.title: Abstract - Bring back those 2007 memories
channel.description:
First off, I wanna state that this is not the best advertisement thread ever, I'm not very good with media, neatness etc.
Second, this is [b]not[/b] a remake, just bringing back some 2007 memories with a rsps twist.
[b][u][size=10pt]FAQ[/size][/u][/b]
[i]Q: Is the base Project Insanity? If so, why?[/i]
[i]A: Yes, because I miss the ORIGINAL Project Insanity, it was actually fun.[/i]
